articles.title: The First 26 Minutes of God of War Ragnarok PC Gameplay - 4K 60FPS Ultra Settings - IGN
articles.description: God of War Ragnarok has now been released on PC and we've got some gameplay for you in glorious 4K 60FPS with all settings maxed out. God of War Ragnarok PC gameplay features options like DLSS, FSR 3.1, Intel XeSS 1.3, and frame generation technology impl…
